{
    "dct_title_s": "Sediment and Water Level Data for the North-South River Estuary and Tidal Marsh, MA, 2018 and 2020",
    "dct_alternative_sm": "North River and South River Estuary Tidal Marsh and Channel Sediment and Water Level Data",
    "dct_description_sm": [
        "Observations from 31 point locations in the North-South Rivers estuary and tidal marsh in the Massachusetts (USA) towns of Marshfield, Scituate, and Norwell. Point location coordinates are provided in a CSV. Additional data tables include: 1) sediment core data, including x-ray fluorescence data, organic content, and foraminifera counts; 2) tidal channel observations of water level and turbidity; and 3) marsh platform observations of water level and turbidity."
    ],
